{"article_id":"ksFZSoWiV5qZN5pI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congress agrees to raise US debt ceiling","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"and provide $ 15bn in hurricane aid","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Congress on Friday approved with bipartisan majorities a budget and hurricane relief deal","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"brokered between Donald Trump and top Democrats .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"By a vote of 316 to 90 , the House of Representatives approved a bill","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to raise the debt ceiling ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"fund the federal government through 8 December","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"and provide $ 15bn for relief from Hurricane Harvey ,","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"which hit Texas and Louisiana last month .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"All 90 votes against came from Republicans .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The deal ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"which was approved by the Senate on Thursday by 80-17 ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"came as Hurricane Irma bore down on Florida .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Here comes Hillary Clinton 's memoir","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"- and there 's plenty of blame","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to go round","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Its genesis was an Oval Office meeting on Wednesday between Trump , treasury secretary Steve Mnuchin , Mike Pence and congressional leaders from both parties .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Trump readily agreed to a Democratic proposal","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"to tie hurricane relief to funding the federal government","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"and increasing the debt ceiling for a three-month period .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Republican leaders had pushed for a longer-term deal ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to raise the debt ceiling through the 2018 midterm elections .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Democrats received rapturously a deal","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Republicans were forced to grudgingly accept .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Many congressional Republicans have long been opposed to raising the debt ceiling","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"without taking steps","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"to reduce federal spending .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Mnuchin and Office of Management and Budget director Mick Mulvaney received a frosty welcome","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"when they pitched the deal to congressional Republicans in a conference meeting on Friday morning .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Mnuchin , a former Democrat , and Mulvaney , a stalwart of the House Freedom Caucus","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"before joining the Trump adminstration ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"made less than ideal surrogates .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"At the meeting , Mnuchin provoked hissing and groans","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"when he closed with a plea","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"for members","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"to \" vote for the debt ceiling for me \" .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"The meeting also got \" a little warm for Mulvaney at times \"","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"according to Mark Walker , a North Carolina representative","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"who noted","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that people in the room \" reminded him [ of ] some of the statements","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"he had made in the past about relief packages","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"tied to the debt ceiling \" .","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"After leaving the meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Mulvaney dodged a question","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"about whether he would have voted for the bill ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"choosing to praise Trump ' s decision","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"to reach across the aisle .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Dreamers condemn","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"'extremely wrong '","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Jeff Sessions :","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"'We 're not taking jobs from anybody '","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Read more","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"\" I thought","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"it was absolutely the right thing","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"to do , \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the former South Carolina congressman said .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"\" The president is a very results driven person ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"he wants to see results . \"","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Peter King , a moderate from New York , saw the vote as a precursor to better days","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"to come .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" We continue to work across the aisle","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"we ' ll get things done ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"we can ' t let one faction control everything , \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"he said in a veiled shot at the Freedom Caucus .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" We represent the country , not a party . \"","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"With these must-pass measures out of the way ,","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"Trump is expected to spend the coming months","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"focusing on promoting his plans for major tax cuts .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"No bill has yet been introduced in Congress","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"but Trump has made several speeches","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"touting his proposals","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"to lower corporate taxes to as little as 15 % .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"On Friday morning , after tweets about hurricane Irma and his frustration with Senate rules and the failure of healthcare reform ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"the president wrote :","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"\" Republicans must start the Tax Reform/Tax Cut legislation ASAP .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Don ' t wait until the end of September .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Needed now more than ever .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Hurry ! \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":80,"right":156,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"N